1
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:20,760
(INDISTINCT TALKING)

2
00:00:35,040 --> 00:00:36,760
I don't think I asked you to sit.

3
00:00:37,360 --> 00:00:39,720
There is a woman who wants to meet you.

4
00:00:39,800 --> 00:00:41,240
That's nice, but I'm married.

5
00:00:41,360 --> 00:00:43,360
Your help is required.

6
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:45,920
I don't discuss my business in public.

7
00:00:46,320 --> 00:00:47,320
I know.

8
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:49,440
(WHOOSHING)

9
00:01:02,440 --> 00:01:04,400
-Who are you?
-A messenger.

10
00:01:04,480 --> 00:01:05,760
Whose messenger?

11
00:01:06,200 --> 00:01:08,400
Darla Von Karlsen.

12
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:11,400
Never heard of her.

13
00:01:14,720 --> 00:01:17,120
-Where's the tea room?
-We were never in the tea room.

14
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:18,960
Oh, of course.

15
00:01:19,800 --> 00:01:23,080
Psychic projection.
Someone sending me a dream message.

16
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:25,520
Well, I hope I fell asleep
somewhere comfy.

17
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:28,040
Do you recognise where you are?

18
00:01:28,960 --> 00:01:30,600
(DISTANT CHILDREN'S LAUGHTER)

19
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:35,960
Can't remember.
How do you hang up on this thing?

20
00:01:36,040 --> 00:01:37,960
-You can't.
-Oh, yeah?

21
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:40,080
And what if I just wake up?

22
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:49,880
No, Doctor, the beach isn't real either.
You are still dreaming.

23
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:53,640
Space-time coordinates.

24
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:57,080
You will meet Darla Von Karlsen here.

25
00:01:58,040 --> 00:02:02,760
Her daughter is in danger.
But only you can save her.

26
00:02:03,960 --> 00:02:06,040
You recognise the planet?

27
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:08,120
Yes.

28
00:02:08,200 --> 00:02:11,080
-Say it, name the planet.
-No. I will not say that.

29
00:02:11,160 --> 00:02:12,160
-Say it!
-No!

30
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,880
Name the planet.

31
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:17,680
(VOICES OVERLAPPING)

32
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:20,600
-Name the planet.
-Skaro.

